OL,6,FVisits are restricted at the Royal
OL,7,FGwent Hospital due to an outbreak of
OL,8,Fnorovirus.
OL,10,FAneurin Bevan University Health Board
OL,11,Fsay there are a "significant" number
OL,12,Fof norovirus cases across patients and
OL,13,Fstaff, with 90 patients and 28 staff
OL,14,Fmembers affected.
