OL,3,CVisits restricted at hospital due to
OL,4,Cnorovirus outbreak
OL,6,F"Visiting with a purpose" restrictions
OL,7,Fwill be in place for the whole
OL,8,Fweekend. This means visits are limited
OL,9,Fto essential wellbeing needs such as
OL,10,Fdelivering fresh clothing and personal
OL,11,Fitems, supporting mental wellbeing,
OL,12,Fand end-of-life care.
OL,14,FPeople are being asked to contact the
OL,15,Fward before visiting, as visitors who
OL,16,Farrive without prior contact may be
OL,17,Fturned away.
