OL,6,FThe Health Board say the decision has
OL,7,Fnot been taken lightly, "but it is
OL,8,Fnecessary to protect the health of our
OL,9,Fpatients and staff and to reduce
OL,10,Ffurther transmission of norovirus,
OL,11,Fwhich is circulating across Gwent."
OL,13,FThey added "norovirus spreads very
OL,14,Feasily and can have a serious impact
OL,15,Fon vulnerable patients and the safe
OL,16,Frunning of our services.
OL,18,F"We know norovirus is circulating
OL,19,Facross our communities and we need
OL,20,Feveryone's support to keep our
OL,21,Fhospitals safe.
