OL,6,FTwo other health boards have been
OL,7,Faffected by norovirus this week.
OL,9,FOn Tuesday, wards had to be closed at
OL,10,Fthe Prince Phillip Hospital in
OL,11,FLlanelli. Four wards were closed, with
OL,12,Ffurther restrictions to the whole
OL,13,Fhospital.
OL,15,FMeanwhile, Cwm Taf Morgannwg
OL,16,FUniversity Health Board also said a
OL,17,Fnumber of their hospitals had been
OL,18,Faffected earlier this week,
OL,19,Fparticularly the Princess of Wales
OL,20,FHospital in Bridgend.
